{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2866a","heading":"Risk-based approach to water management and water security at military installations","label":"2866a Risk-based approach to water management and water security at military installations","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptIV/ch169/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe date of the enactment of this section, referred to in subsec. (g), is the date of enactment of , which was approved on .Pub. L. 119–60Dec. 18, 2025Section 2827 of the Military Construction Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2021, referred to in subsec. (h), is , which was formerly set out as a note under , prior to repeal by , , .section 2827 of div. B of Pub. L. 116–283section 2866 of this titlePub. L. 119–60, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2804(b)139 Stat. 1297Dec. 18, 2025"],"amendments":["References in TextThe date of the enactment of this section, referred to in subsec. (g), is the date of enactment of , which was approved on .Pub. L. 119–60Dec. 18, 2025Section 2827 of the Military Construction Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2021, referred to in subsec. (h), is , which was formerly set out as a note under , prior to repeal by , , .section 2827 of div. B of Pub. L. 116–283section 2866 of this titlePub. L. 119–60, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2804(b)139 Stat. 1297Dec. 18, 2025"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—In General","label":"a .—In General","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Defense shall adopt a risk-based approach to water management and water security for each military installation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are experiencing the greatest risks to water management and water security; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"face, or potentially face, the most severe adverse effects on mission assurance because of such risks.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Determinations under paragraph (2) shall be made on the basis of the water management and water security assessments made by the Secretary concerned under subsection (b).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Water Management and Water Security Assessments","label":"b .—Water Management and Water Security Assessments","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"risks to water management and water security; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2866a%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"adverse effects on mission assurance because of such risks.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2866a/b","sourceUrl":"http